      <widget>
	<class>GtkLabel</class>
	<child_name>Notebook:tab</child_name>
	<name>event_editor_label</name>
	<label>Event Editor</label>
	<justify>GTK_JUSTIFY_CENTER</justify>
	<wrap>False</wrap>
	<xalign>0.5</xalign>
	<yalign>0.5</yalign>
	<xpad>0</xpad>
	<ypad>0</ypad>
      </widget>

      <widget>
	<class>GtkScrolledWindow</class>
	<name>event_api_reference_scrolledwindow</name>
	<hscrollbar_policy>GTK_POLICY_AUTOMATIC</hscrollbar_policy>
	<vscrollbar_policy>GTK_POLICY_ALWAYS</vscrollbar_policy>
	<hupdate_policy>GTK_UPDATE_CONTINUOUS</hupdate_policy>
	<vupdate_policy>GTK_UPDATE_CONTINUOUS</vupdate_policy>

	<widget>
	  <class>GtkText</class>
	  <name>event_api_reference_textbox</name>
	  <can_focus>True</can_focus>
	  <editable>False</editable>
	  <text>All Events must adhere to the following EBNF Grammar:

&lt;Action&gt; &lt;Object&gt; [&lt;Preposition&gt; &lt;Object&gt;]
[ '('Requires [! | '('Not')'] &lt;Requirement&gt;')' ]
{ ( and | or ) '('Requires [! | '('Not')'] &lt;Requirement&gt;')' } -&gt;
	&lt;Effect&gt; {and &lt;Effect&gt;};

Actions:
Get
Drop
( and any User-Defined Verb in the Verb Text File)

Refs:          // References to Objects
'(' int ')'    // Reference to Object's Number
'[' int - string ']' // Reference to Object's Number and Name

Prepositions:
with
on
from
to
etc. (Any word or string of characters, without any spaces)

Objects:
Item&lt;Ref&gt;
Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt;

Requirements:
PlayerPoints'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerExp'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerHP'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerMP'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerStr'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerIQ'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerDex'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerAgil'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerCharisma'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerArmorLevel'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerCurrentWeight'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
Room&lt;Ref&gt;IsCurrentRoom
Room&lt;Ref&gt;HasVisited
Item&lt;Ref&gt;InInventory
Item&lt;Ref&gt;IsEquipped
Item&lt;Ref&gt;ExistsInRoom&lt;Ref&gt;
Item&lt;Ref&gt;Weight'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
Item&lt;Ref&gt;Bulk'['&lt;Comparison&gt;'](' int ')'
Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt;ExistsInRoom&lt;Ref&gt;
Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt;ExistsInRoom&lt;Ref&gt;Direction&lt;Ref&gt;
Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt;IsVisible

Effects:
Adds Item&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;Preposition&gt; &lt;ItemLocation&gt;
Adds Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;Preposition&gt; Room&lt;Ref&gt;Direction&lt;Ref&gt;
Removes Item&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;Preposition&gt; &lt;ItemLocation&gt;
Removes Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;Preposition&gt; Room&lt;Ref&gt;Direction&lt;Ref&gt;
Modifies Player &lt;PlayerAttributes&gt;
Modifies Room&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;RoomAttributes&gt;
Modifies Item&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;ItemAttributes&gt;
Modifies Obstruction&lt;Ref&gt; &lt;ObstructionAttributes&gt;
TextMessage'[' string Message ']'
GraphicMessage'[' URL, int, int ']' // [Graphic URL, X-coordinate, Y-coordinate]

ItemLocations:
Inventory
CurrentRoom
Room&lt;Ref&gt;

PlayerAttributes:
PlayerPoints'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerExp'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerHP'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerMP'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerStr'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerIQ'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerDex'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerAgil'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerCharisma'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerArmorLevel'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'
PlayerCurrentWeight'['&lt;Expression&gt;'](' int ')'

RoomAttributes:
TextDescription'('Long')[' string ']'
TextDescription'('Short')[' string ']'
DirectionDescription'[' string ']'
GraphicURL'[' URL ']'
Visited'(' boolean ')'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;ToWhichRoom'(' int ')'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;FirstTransitionText'[' string ']'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;TransitionText'[' string ']'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;FirstTransitionGraphic'[' URL ']'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;TransitionGraphic'[' URL ']'
DirectionObject&lt;Ref&gt;HasMovedThisWay'(' boolean ')'

ItemAttributes:
Equipped'(' boolean ')'
Weight'(' int ')'
Bulk'(' int ')'
TextDescription'[' string ']'
Environment_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'
Environment_GraphicPos'(' int , int ')' // (X-coordinate, Y-coordinate)
CloseUp_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'
Icon_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'
Equipped_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'

ObstructionAttributes:
Visible'(' boolean ')'
TextDescription'[' string ']'
Environment_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'
Environment_GraphicPos'(' int , int ')' // (X-coordinate, Y-coordinate)
CloseUp_GraphicURL'[' URL ']'

Comparisons:
==
!=
&gt;
&lt;
&gt;=
&lt;=

Expressions:
=
+
-
</text>
	</widget>
      </widget>

      <widget>
	<class>GtkLabel</class>
	<child_name>Notebook:tab</child_name>
	<name>event_api_reference_label</name>
	<label>Event API Reference</label>
	<justify>GTK_JUSTIFY_CENTER</justify>
	<wrap>False</wrap>
	<xalign>0.5</xalign>
	<yalign>0.5</yalign>
	<xpad>0</xpad>
	<ypad>0</ypad>
      </widget>
    </widget>
  </widget>
</widget>

